descript.abstract: This is a detailed polygon shapefile of the recognized neighborhood association boundaries.
descript.purpose: To show the neighborhood association boundaries within the city of Sacramento.
descript.supplinf:
The boundaries contained within this file are NOT determined by the City of Sacramento or city staff. These boundaries are defined by the respective associations and groups included within the file. Neighborhood Services Department has worked extensively with representatives of each individual neighborhood association to confirm the boundaries.
Note: There are many cases in which multiple polygons are covering the same area. Symbology is important to consider when using this file.
